name: IBIF v2 - all pressures - biodiversity intactness - overall
description: Intactness-based Biodiversity Impact Factors (IBIF) for all environmental pressures (GHG as CO2-eq, NH3, NOx emissions and land occupation) impacts on terrestrial biodiversity intactness, (overall). Land occupation converted from km2 to m2 to match ecoinvent units. Based on GLOBIO 4 model and Mean Species Abundance (MSA) metric. From Schipper et al. 2025: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-025-05946-1
